column2: ALPHA TO BRAVO. OK LETS START THIS OPERATION. OVER.
ALPHA BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE REACHED OUT OBJECTIVE. OVER.
PAPA BEAR TO ALPHA. COPY. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OVER.
THIS IS DELTA BLACK ONE CALLING ALPHA SQUAD. GET READY FOR TRANSPORT. OVER.
DELTA TO ALPHA. HEADS UP. APPROACHING LANDING ZONE, GET READY TO DISEMBARK. OVER.
GOOD LUCK ALPHA. SHOW THEM HELL. DELTA BLACK OUT.
